      "body": "Hey there,\n\nMy name is [Your Name] and I'm the Conversion Copywriter here at OLYMPUS. I wanted to personally welcome you to the Build Console and let you know what's in store.\n\nOver the next few days, I'll be sending you some tips and strategies to help you get the most out of this powerful tool. But first, let me ask - what's your biggest pain point when it comes to managing your builds right now?\n\nIs it the lack of visibility into what's happening? The constant context-switching between different tools and dashboards? Or maybe it's the challenge of keeping your team aligned and on the same page.\n\nWhichever it is, I can assure you that the Build Console was designed to solve those exact problems. Our team of OLYMPUS experts has poured their hearts into creating an intuitive, all-in-one solution that gives you total control over your build process.\n\nStay tuned for more - I'll be sharing some eye-opening insights that I guarantee will transform the way you approach your builds.\n\nCheers,\n[Your Name]\nConversion Copywriter, OLYMPUS",
